# Using CLI

- `gh project list`
    number of the project and id of project

- `gh project field-list 4 --owner sergiorgiraldo`
    id of 'status' field

- `gh project field-list 4 --owner sergiorgiraldo --format json --jq '.fields[]|select(.name == "Status")|.options'`
    get id of options

- `gh project item-list 4 --owner sergiorgiraldo`
    get id of ticket

- `gh project item-edit --project-id PVT_kwHOABF2LM4A9Hmr --id PVTI_lAHOABF2LM4A9HmrzgcRRzc --field-id PVTSSF_lAHOABF2LM4A9Hmrzgw6qCk --single-select-option-id 98236657`
    update to "Done"
